-- Qantas: current trading good, confident on future
-- 
-- Mon Jul 28, 2008 1:27am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/07/28/us-qantas-outlook-idUSSYA00444320080728

 

 SYDNEY  (Reuters) - Qantas Airways Ltd ( QAN.AX ) Chief Executive Geoff Dixon said on Monday that the airline was trading well in difficult conditions, and was confident for the future. 

 Dixon made the comments at a media briefing following an announcement earlier on Monday that he will retire from the top job at Australia's national airline. (Reporting by  Jonathan Standing )